libs.content:
find_program(krb5_config names krb5-config heimdal-krb5-config paths
     /opt/local/bin
     only_cmake_find_root_path               
  )

find_program(touch_executable touch doc "path to touch executable"
        paths "c:/program files/git/usr/bin"
              "c:/program files (x86)/git/usr/bin")

find_program(signtool_executable signtool 
      paths "$env{programfiles}/microsoft sdks/windows/v7.0a/bin"
      "$env{programfiles}/windows kits/8.0/bin/x86"
      "$env{programfiles}/windows kits/8.1/bin/x86"
    )
find_program(cat_executable cat doc "path to the executable")

find_library(wix_wcautil_library 
  names wcautilx86  wcautilvs2015x86
  wcautil
  paths 
  ${wix_dir}/../sdk/vs2015/lib/x86
  )

find_library(odbc_library
    names odbc odbcinst odbc32
    paths
    /usr/lib
    /usr/lib/odbc
    /usr/local/lib
    /usr/local/lib/odbc
    /usr/local/odbc/lib
    
    
    
    
    
    doc "specify the odbc driver manager library here."
    )

find_library(iconv_libraries names iconv libiconv paths
               /usr/lib/
               no_cmake_system_path)
